General.Name: Prestige Wealth Inc. Ordinary Shares
General.Description: Prestige Wealth Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides wealth management and asset management services in Hong Kong. The company assists its clients in identifying and purchasing wealth and asset management products. It offers its services to high net worth and ultra-high net worth individuals, including business owners, executives, heirs of rich families, and other affluent individuals residing in mainland China or Hong Kong; and enterprises. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Central, Hong Kong. Prestige Wealth Inc. is a subsidiary of Prestige Financial Holdings Group Limited.
